@F read.flow v1.0 2026-01-13
= absorption > scanning â€” reading books

intent
  fetch "books" (Project Gutenberg)
  index "chapters"
  track "progress"

logic
  input: id or name
  
  mode list
    show library/books content
    
  mode fetch(id)
    download from gutenberg
    clean headers/footers
    save to library
    
  mode read
    load text
    paginate or chapter-select
    fix unicode

commands
  py read <id>               | fetch book
  py read <name>             | read book
  py read <name> --chapter N | read specific chapter

integration
  Urllib (fetch)
  SovereignAgent (library path)
